    "The increasing occurrences highlight the dynamic nature of research in energy technologies and the continuous efforts to innovate and improve these systems.As seen in the Fig. 11, two major research areas are highlighted; the red coloured cluster represents wind energy systems and control of DFIG especially in a practical approach using MATLAB and controllers.",
